          <updateDate>2017-11-15T05:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Pell for Performance Act</b></p> <p>This bill amends the Higher Education Act of 1965 to modify the Federal Pell Grant program. Specifically, if a Pell Grant recipient fails to complete an education program within the maximum timeframe for completion, then the Pell Grants received for such program convert to a Federal Direct Unsubsidized Stafford Loan and are subject to repayment, in accordance with applicable terms and conditions.</p>]]></text>
          <actionDate>2017-11-15</actionDate>
        </item>
